Lis running services       systemctl -t service --state=active

Stop / start service       systemctl stop name.service
                           systemctl start  name.service

enable / disable service   systemctl enable name.service
                           systemctl disable name.service

Reboot                     systemctl shutdown / poweroff
                           systemctl  reboot

Yum command                yum install
                           yum info
                           yum module list
                           yum module info modulename
